{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"PSD SDC Toolkits","description":"PSD SDC Toolkits."}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Ghost Admin","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"Ghost Admin - Core Concepts","meta_description":"Ghost is installed with a streamlined clientside admin interface for editors who need a powerful tool to manage their content.","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"concepts","toc":null,"keywords":["concepts","ghost","publishing","architecture"]},"html":"<p>A streamlined clientside admin interface for editors who need a powerful tool to manage their content.</p>\n<p>Traditionally, people writing content and people writing code rarely agree on the best platform to use. Tools with great editors generally lack speed and extensibility, and speedy frameworks basically always sacrifice user experience.</p>\n<h2 id=\"overview\"><a href=\"#overview\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Overview</h2>\n<p>Thanks to its decoupled architecture Ghost is able to have the best of both worlds. Ghost-Admin is a completely independent client application to the Ghost Core API which doesn't have any impact on performance. And, writers don't need to suffer their way through learning Git just to publish a new post.</p>\n<p>Great for editors. Great for developers. Also available as <a href=\"/concepts/https://ghost.org/downloads_zh_CN\">Desktop App</a>.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/0d983/ghost-admin.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 650px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 62.70232230823364%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/d19d2/ghost-admin.webp 163w,\n/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/9c1cd/ghost-admin.webp 325w,\n/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/bc0ed/ghost-admin.webp 650w,\n/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/e5b2b/ghost-admin.webp 975w,\n/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/6977a/ghost-admin.webp 1300w,\n/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/a6f35/ghost-admin.webp 1421w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/5e27a/ghost-admin.png 163w,\n/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/034ef/ghost-admin.png 325w,\n/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/59fd5/ghost-admin.png 650w,\n/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/d1e75/ghost-admin.png 975w,\n/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/c57c3/ghost-admin.png 1300w,\n/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/0d983/ghost-admin.png 1421w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/2330647cf02e09731e52590745fef1f7/59fd5/ghost-admin.png\"\n          alt=\"Ghost Admin\"\n          title=\"\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2 id=\"publishing-workflow\"><a href=\"#publishing-workflow\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Publishing workflow</h2>\n<p>Hacking together some Markdown files and throwing a static-site generator on top is nice in theory, but anyone who has tried to manage a content archive knows how quickly this falls apart under even light usage. What happens when you want to schedule a post to be published on Monday?</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/64e88b17e2a6d2f2b0626b866c806dcc/3674b/publishing-workflow.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 650px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 53.434065934065934%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/64e88b17e2a6d2f2b0626b866c806dcc/d19d2/publishing-workflow.webp 163w,\n/static/64e88b17e2a6d2f2b0626b866c806dcc/9c1cd/publishing-workflow.webp 325w,\n/static/64e88b17e2a6d2f2b0626b866c806dcc/bc0ed/publishing-workflow.webp 650w,\n/static/64e88b17e2a6d2f2b0626b866c806dcc/66a44/publishing-workflow.webp 728w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/64e88b17e2a6d2f2b0626b866c806dcc/5e27a/publishing-workflow.png 163w,\n/static/64e88b17e2a6d2f2b0626b866c806dcc/034ef/publishing-workflow.png 325w,\n/static/64e88b17e2a6d2f2b0626b866c806dcc/59fd5/publishing-workflow.png 650w,\n/static/64e88b17e2a6d2f2b0626b866c806dcc/3674b/publishing-workflow.png 728w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/64e88b17e2a6d2f2b0626b866c806dcc/59fd5/publishing-workflow.png\"\n          alt=\"Publishing Worfklow\"\n          title=\"\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>Great editorial teams need proper tools which help them be effective, which is why Ghost-Admin has all the standard editorial workflow features available at the click of a button. From inputting custom social and SEO data to customising exactly how and where content will be output.</p>\n<h2 id=\"best-in-class-editor\"><a href=\"#best-in-class-editor\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Best-in-class editor</h2>\n<p>Ghost Admin also comes with a world-class editor for authoring posts, which is directly tied to a rock-solid document storage format. More on that a bit later!</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/77ed7/ghost-admin-editor.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 650px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.01941747572816%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/d19d2/ghost-admin-editor.webp 163w,\n/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/9c1cd/ghost-admin-editor.webp 325w,\n/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/bc0ed/ghost-admin-editor.webp 650w,\n/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/e5b2b/ghost-admin-editor.webp 975w,\n/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/1b867/ghost-admin-editor.webp 1236w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/5e27a/ghost-admin-editor.png 163w,\n/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/034ef/ghost-admin-editor.png 325w,\n/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/59fd5/ghost-admin-editor.png 650w,\n/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/d1e75/ghost-admin-editor.png 975w,\n/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/77ed7/ghost-admin-editor.png 1236w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/7eb8c59af6f0177a1ac46f7641ca4f9c/59fd5/ghost-admin-editor.png\"\n          alt=\"Ghost Editor\"\n          title=\"\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>But, our default client app isn't the only way to interact write content to the Ghost <a href=\"/concepts//api/admin_zh_CN\">Admin API</a>. You can send data into Ghost from pretty much anywhere, or even write your own custom admin client if you have a particular usecase which requires it.</p>\n<p>Ghost-Admin is extremely powerful but entirely optional.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/concepts/admin/"},"timeToRead":2,"excerpt":"A streamlined clientside admin interface for editors who need a powerful tool to manage their content. Traditionally, people writing content…","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/gavinwang/Documents/Working/codes/sdc_toolkits/content/concepts/admin.md"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/concepts/admin/"}}